                <p>SQL 数据库提供内置数据支持，能够为任何时长最多 35 天的事务进行数据的时点还原。此外，你还可自动复制到你选择的其他 Azure 区域。这可让你轻松实现针对你的业务需求设计的灾难恢复策略。</p> -->
                <p>Azure SQL Database is a cloud database service built for <strong>application developers</strong>. The database is a unique service that allows <a href="https://docs.azure.cn/zh-cn/sql-database/sql-database-service-tiers" id="home-sql_sql-database-service-tiers">real time scaling without downtime</a>, helps you to efficiently deliver multi-tenant applications, and further enables you more time to innovate and release products to the market at a faster speed. The <strong>built-in intelligence</strong> of the SQL database will quickly <a href="https://docs.azure.cn/zh-cn/sql-database/sql-database-advisor" id="home-sql_sql-database-advisor">understand the unique characteristics of the application and dynamically adjust it</a> to maximize its performance, reliability, and data protection capabilities. You can use <a href="https://docs.azure.cn/zh-cn/sql-database/sql-database-develop-overview" id="home-sql_sql-database-develop-overview">a language and platform you like to generate secure applications</a> which shall be connected to an SQL database.</p>
