                    <h3>Active Geo-replication</h3>
                    <p>Active Geo-replication can create up to 4 online (readable) secondary databases in any Azure region. The secondary database can be created using the same service level as the primary database, with some potential differences in performance. The secondary database is priced at 1 times the price of the selected performance level. The traffic costs arising from Geo-replication between the primary and secondary databases are included in the costs of the online secondary database.</p>
