                <h2>Support and Service Level Agreements</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions or need help, please visit <a href="/support/contact/" id="database-contact-page">Azure Support</a> and select self-help service or any other method to contact us for support.</p>
				<p>Basic, Standard, and Advanced Levels</p>
				<p>We guarantee that the connection between a single or elastic basic, standard or advanced Azure SQL Database and our Internet gateway is not less than 99.99% of the time.</p>
				<p>Web and Enterprise Editions (out of service)</p>
				<p>We ensure customers will be able to establish a connection between the Web Edition or Enterprise Edition Azure SQL Database and our Internet gateway at least 99.9% of the time.</p>
